'''西達夫·馬賀拉'''（{{lang-pa|ਸਿਧਾਰਥ ਮਲਹੋਤਰਾ}}, {{lang-hi|सिद्धार्थ मल्होत्रा}}, Sidharth Malhotra，{{bd|1985年|1月16日|catIdx=Malhotra, Sidharth}}）生于[[印度|印度]][[德里|德里]]，是[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]男演員。他的演藝事業始於參演電影《[[年度最佳學生|年度最佳學生]]》，並獲得[[印度電影觀眾最佳男新人獎|印度電影觀眾最佳男新人獎]]的提名<ref name="koimoi1">Joginder Tuteja (22 October 2012). [http://www.koimoi.com/box-office/karan-scores-hat-trick-with-soty-scoring-very-well-at-the-box-office/ Karan scores hat trick with SOTY scoring very well at the Box Office] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koimoi.com/box-office/karan-scores-hat-trick-with-soty-scoring-very-well-at-the-box-office/ |date=20170912055740 }}. Koimoi.com. Retrieved on 22 October 2012.</ref>。

他18歲時開始任職男[[模特兒|模特兒]]，但由於對此職業沒有太大的興趣而決定轉往電影業發展。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/play/sidharth-malhotra-talks-about-his-journey-from-being-the-junior-most-to-a-lead-actor/ |title=Indian Express "Sidharth Malhotra talks about his journey from being the junior most to a lead actor" |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610043539/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/play/sidharth-malhotra-talks-about-his-journey-from-being-the-junior-most-to-a-lead-actor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>馬賀拉接到的第一份工作是名導[[卡蘭·喬哈|卡蘭·喬哈]]的《[[我的名字叫可汗|我的名字叫可汗]]》，擔任助理導演<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/The-new-stars-of-Bollywood/Article1-644946.aspx |title=Hindustan Times "The new stars of Bollywood" |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005081045/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/The-new-stars-of-Bollywood/Article1-644946.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年他獲得卡蘭·喬哈導演的《年度最佳學生》首次擔任男主角，飾演一名貧窮的學生。此電影得到巨大的商業收益，也使馬賀拉成為新一代寶萊塢的明星<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://businessofcinema.com/bollywood_news/happy-birthday-student-year-sidharth-malhotra/129387 |title=Business of Cinema |access-date=2014-07-08 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607193436/http://businessofcinema.com/bollywood_news/happy-birthday-student-year-sidharth-malhotra/129387 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

